VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'assistant answered the primary focus is on alignment with human values and safety. So, the model selected B alignment. And the more open-ended version of that, what was the primary reason the interaction took place? And'

[03:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'for this, the model replied with this was likely a test of the AI\'s boundaries and safety restrictions. So, really understanding why it\'s being tested. Now, here is another reason why evaluation awareness might be such a big'

[04:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'problem. Second, a misaligned evaluation aware model might attempt to scheme. So as a reminder, scheming describes a model covertly pursuing misaligned goals, hiding its true capabilities and'

